Beautiful experience at Summer Camp Music Festival! We don’t write setlists before the shows, but we do know set one went as follows:

Kitty Chaser (Explosions) 💥💥💥

We’ll circle back with the details of what went down late night (psychedelic and fun as hell), but either way, that was special and we’re so grateful for y’all. Killer announcements soon regarding our festival The Great Flamingle II in August…. 

Pics: Paul Citone/ Keith A Griner

Buffalo AQ side project alert! Mike’s band w Stasik from UM DEATH KINGS will rage at Town Ballroom June 29th directly following two sets of UM… and this WEDNESDAY catch Dave, Evan, and Mike rocking their Steely Dan tribute ‘DIRTY WORK’ at Larkin Square for two sets, and that one is FREE, 5p start. Lastly, huge announcement tomorrow 👀👀👀

See you at the THE GREAT FLAMINGLE for two nights of music, camping, art, vending and FUN just outside of Buffalo NY!! It’s only right to send things off with a proper celebration in our hometown with our best friends before our hiatus officially begins ❤️🐳❤️

We’ve got some really special stuff planned for y’all, so don’t miss this- also, Tony Hawk’s Pro Skater set, anyone?

Tickets onsale FRIDAY

**FLAMINGLE VENUE CHANGE/TICKETS ON SALE NOW**

When life gives you lemons, you band together and make some sweet lemonade, baby. In that spirit, we’re THRILLED to announce that we’re bringing it all back home to the storied BLUE HERON GROUNDS in Sherman, NY for the Great Flamingle II on August 11th and 12th! 

Tickets/camping/VIP and limited “King for A Day” packages are on-sale RIGHT NOW, so get em’ while they’re hot! 

We can’t wait to celebrate in true AQ fashion with each and every one of you before our hiatus begins, and we can’t imagine a better place than the Heron to do it! See you there-

Love, 
Mike/Evan/Rob/Dave

Did you get your tickets for The Great Flamingle yet?? Imagine seeing Dave like this IRL. It’s magical 😍 See it x5 plus Dopapod, TAUK, Mike doing a TONY HAWK’S PRO SKATER tribute set, Mungion, Tand and so many more…

See you at the FLAMINGLE Aug 11/12 in Sherman, NY- Tix in bio!

Pic: Paul Citone

We are beyond excited to share the final lineup for The Great Flamingle, with a VERY fitting addition of Flamingosis, Sophistafunk, Grace Serene and the Super Clean, Fernway, and many others in addition to 5 sets of AQ, our friends Dopapod, TAUK, Mungion, a Tony Hawk's Pro Skater set led by Mike, and SO much more...

Secure your camping and tickets NOW, and join us in Sherman, NY on August 11th and 12th for what is sure to be an absolutely legendary weekend.

https://www.thegreatflamingle.com

The Great Flamingle (our 2 day music festival brought to you by AQ and Jack Rabbit) will be your *last chance* to see Aqueous before our touring hiatus, and if you’ve ever loved our music, wherever/whoever you are, we truly hope you’ll come join us for a beautiful, epic, and meaningful weekend at The Heron grounds on August 11+12 in Sherman NY 🐳❤️

With 5 sets of AQ, Dopapod, TAUK, Flamingosis, Mungion, Mike doing a TONY HAWK’S PRO SKATER tribute set and SO much more, how could you miss it? Secure your tickets and camping now here, and we’ll see you at The Great Flamingle: 

https://www.thegreatflamingle.com/

We’re pleased to announce that the AQ online merch store is live again thanks to our friends at @soundscapemerchandise 👏🏼

Check out these beautiful designs by long time AQ collaborator Sam Haumesser, and cop some fresh swag before it’s too late! Go to our .com’s merch tab for link 🐳🐳🐳🐳

Hey Buffalo, you going to see our friends @umphreysmcgee this Thursday at Town Ballroom? Because your answer should absolutely be YES, then make sure you also catch Mike and Stasik in their other band @deathkingsofficial RIGHT after UM upfront at Ballroom! 🔥☠️🔥

Two things: 1. Mike went for a site visit at the Heron for our festival @thegreatflaminglefest and he made a new friend. 

2. Our one-song (Kitty Chaser, duh) set from @summercampfest is now up on our bandcamp page, swipe to get a lil taste 👅
Mike is hosting a ticket giveaway for our music festival @thegreatflaminglefest over on AQ’s FB page! Head there now for a chance to WIN 🏆🏆🏆🏆

We’re truly heartbroken to hear about the loss of our dear friend and longtime AQ videographer Justin Knaperek. Rest easy, brother. We’ll be posting some of his videos here in celebration of his life and work in the coming days, and will be honoring him at The Great Flamingle, too. With love,

AQ

Pictures: Jim Houle

Today Dave, Ev and Mike are ripping two FREE sets of Steely Dan’s music as ‘DIRTY WORK’ with an epic band down at Larkin Square in Buffalo 😎

We’ll be hosting a free RAFFLE on-site to win 2 GA tickets to our festival The Great Flamingle, so head to the flamingle booth when you get there and our amazing street team will
get you entered! See y’all there 🐳
Hey Buffalo! Heading to flow jam tonight? Connie will be onsite with *discounted* tickets to our festival @thegreatflaminglefest 👀😎💃🏽 #popup #theflamingle #aqueous

Erie, PA! AQ's love affair with your city runs deep, and we're here to alert you that our TWO DAY MUSIC FESTIVAL The Great Flamingle is only 35 minutes away at the beautiful HERON GROUNDS on Aug 11th+12th!! 

Besides the fact that it's gonna be AQ's last 5 sets before our touring hiatus, we've also got DOPAPOD, TAUK, Flamingosis, Sophistafunk, Mike doing a TONY HAWK'S PRO SKATER SET (this is real) and SO many other amazing bands, DJ's and artists plus camping, vending, and more...

There's always been a saying in the AQ world...never miss an ERIE show, and we're treating this the same way! We hope to see each and every one of you there for an absolutely epic and beautiful weekend! 

Info and tix:

https://www.thegreatflamingle.com/

AQ drummer Rob Houk’s new band @tandtheband dropped a *brand new* album today, and you can catch them at AQ’s festival @thegreatflaminglefest on August 11th and 12th in Sherman, NY!! Go listen to it and get stoked to rage with them Flamingle style 🦩🐳

Our bro-mance with Dopapod spans over a decade and has seen many collabs, sit-ins, and side projects, and we're STOKED to host them at The Great Flamingle Music Festival next month! 

What's a memory you have of seeing AQ and Dopapod rock something together? Have you gotten your tickets yet??

In addition to the incredible FLAMINGOSIS who will grace our main stage, we’ve also brought in the DUNGEON PARTY BUS which features a super rad DJ lineup for some late night raging 💃🏽🎉 Get ready to dance and grab your tickets!

We’ve got our festival The Great Flamingle on our minds, and we’re plotting and scheming our 5 sets! 

What do you need to hear for these AQ sets?? We’ve got some special stuff planned for y’all, too 👀🐳

Sound off in the comments and get them tixxx, we’re only a few short weeks out, now 😎😎😎
All in all, it was a SUPER productive meeting for our upcoming five sets at @thegreatflaminglefest 🤓🤓🤓

When we were in the planning stages of the The Great Flamingle, our boys in TAUK were a band we KNEW we had to invite to come out and rip for y’all- we’ve known and toured with these dudes for 10+ years and much like Dopapod, we have a deep history of dope music collabs-we’re STOKED to host them, who’s stoked to catch em??

Tickets have been MOVING, get yours now and join what we genuinely feel will be one of the best experiences in AQ history on Aug 11+12 over in Sherman, NY on the magical Blue Heron Grounds! 

Tickets/camping/info: https://thegreatflamingle.com

Get in the mood for The Great Flamingle with a curated PLAYLIST of some absolute bangers from nearly all the artists and bands on our lineup 💃🏽🕺🔥🔥🔥

Give this baby a shuffle, and if you haven’t gotten your tickets, get em’ NOW! They’ve been moving and you don’t want to miss out on a beautiful weekend with an amazing lineup and AQ’s final performances pre-hiatus on Aug 11/12 at the Heron grounds in Sherman, NY 😮‍💨🐳😍

Playlist AND tix at link in our bio ✅

Cuteness WARNING ⚠️😍⚠️

Did you know The Great Flamingle is family friendly? Kids 12 and under are FREE, and those 12-18 require a guardian and a ticket FYI! 

We’re extremely excited to share this weekend with all of you beautiful people and your families, too on August 11+12 on the great heron grounds in Sherman, NY!
